{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"3316","heading":"Submission of intelligence community policies","label":"3316 Submission of intelligence community policies","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3316","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t50/ch45/schI","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft50%2Fs3316","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","DefinitionsFor definitions of “intelligence community” and “congressional intelligence committees” as used in this section, see , set out as a note under .section 5003 of div. E of Pub. L. 116–92section 3003 of this title"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Definitions","label":"a Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3316/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3316","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft50%2Fs3316%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Electronic repository","label":"1 Electronic repository","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3316/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3316/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft50%2Fs3316%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “electronic repository” means the electronic distribution mechanism, in use as of , or any successor electronic distribution mechanism, by which the Director of National Intelligence submits to the congressional intelligence committees information.December 20, 2019","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Policy","label":"2 Policy","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3316/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3316/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft50%2Fs3316%2Fa%2F2","sourceReleas